[
  {
    "key": "eb383fcf15b30260c90f3fa460f551c7117f59048bc273743b0c787f1b68cec5",
    "original": " days in total without at least ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"%OOC%How this origin works:%OOC_OFF%\\n- It's all about teaching your students. The game will end if you spend \" + avatarEffect.m.DaysWithoutRecruitsMax + \" days in total without at least \" + avatarEffect.m.NumRecruitsRequired - 1 + \" other recruits.\\n- Recruits gain the 'Swordmaster's Training' effect which grants special bonuses when using swords and gets stronger with every level.\\n- Recruits with access to the Sword perk group have a \" + recruitEffect.m.FreePerkChancePerLevel + \"% chance to gain a free sword perk upon leveling up.\\n- Recruits who come with access to the Sword perk group lose all other weapon perk groups and gain access to the Swordmaster perk group with special perks related to swordfighting to allow for a variety of different specializations and fighting styles.\\n- Cannot equip any weapon except swords, banner, or a ranged weapon.\\n- Remember to check the tooltip of the 'Swordmaster's Training' or 'Swordmaster's Finesse' effects on your characters for important information regarding their bonuses (and penalties if applicable).\\n- Limited to \" + origin.m.BrothersMax + \" total characters and maximum \" + origin.m.BrothersMaxInCombat + \" in battle.\\n- The main character will get exhausted after every battle and will need a few days to get back in fighting shape. He will also get older over time and get various penalties.\\n- Highly talented recruits can challenge swordmasters at settlements, and if successful, gain strong bonuses.\\n- Character backgrounds highly proficient in melee combat are not recruitable.\\n- The world tests your steel without restraint. Combat difficulty scales faster in this origin than usual, resulting in contracts being more deadly.\\n- The Fountain of Youth (Grotesque Tree) location does not exist in this origin.\\n- Named weapon drops from locations are more likely to be swords.\""
  },
